text: Hi Chris et al - Roger Strukhoff here from Altoros. I work for Renat and Andrei as Director of Research and want to grab the whitepaper by the horns and make it hyperledger-centric instead of OBC-repurposed. Any guidance on how I can get started doing this?
Also interested in really fleshing out at least some of the nascent use cases. My thinking is to attend the Thursday call and see if I can get a direction down this path as well. Thx.
